text:
In http://poi.apache.org/spreadsheet/quick-guide.html in the section "Getting the cell contents" the code refers to a class "DateUtil" which does not seem to exist in poi 3.2-FINAL-20081019.
Unless this is a change that hasn't been officially released, this tutorial seems to be incorrect and should probably refer to "HSSFDateUtil" intstead.
